flowchart LR
    A[Developer opens or updates PR] --> B[GitHub Action starts]
    B --> C[Checkout repository]
    C --> D[Generate pr_diff.patch]
    D --> E[Run unit tests + coverage]
    D --> F[Run Android lint]
    E --> G[Coverage context]
    F --> H[Lint context]
    G --> I[run_agent.py orchestrator]
    H --> I
    D --> I

    I --> J[Master Reviewer Agent]
    J --> K[Architecture / Logic Agent]
    J --> L[Compose UI Agent]
    J --> M[Security / Config Agent]
    J --> N[Test / QA Agent]

    K --> O[Structured XML findings]
    L --> O
    M --> O
    N --> O

    O --> P[Parse file + line + severity]
    P --> Q[Map findings to changed diff lines]
    Q --> R[Create inline GitHub PR review comments]
    G --> S[Coverage alert comments for logic files]
    R --> T[Developer fixes issues]
    S --> T
    T --> U[Human reviewer focuses on higher-value review]

